4
00:00:07,200 --> 00:00:10,800
It can lead to anxiety, stress, and even burnout.

5
00:00:10,800 --> 00:00:11,600
But why?

6
00:00:11,600 --> 00:00:15,600
Studies show it's linked to personality traits and social dynamics.

7
00:00:15,600 --> 00:00:19,200
Understanding this can be the key to overcoming self-doubt.

